{"tid":1787092,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"段崇智膺泰晤士高等教育風雲人物　評選記者：堅定為校園學生挺身而出","createTime":"2019-12-17T15:53:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T16:00:37.000Z","uid":301388,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2ebda2ee95fd461223fa8c635c628382aa452ee9","tid":1787092,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:53:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191217/s00001/1576587937393/段崇智膺泰晤士高等教育風雲人物-評選記者-堅定為校園學生挺身而出\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191217%2Fs00001%2F1576587937393%2F%E6%AE%B5%E5%B4%87%E6%99%BA%E8%86%BA%E6%B3%B0%E6%99%A4%E5%A3%AB%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9-%E8%A9%95%E9%81%B8%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-%E5%A0%85%E5%AE%9A%E7%82%BA%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%8C%BA%E8%BA%AB%E8%80%8C%E5%87%BA&d=hjTGTk%2FOBCUjzD4XQyU%2Bunr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=60f1f449\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191217%2Fs00001%2F1576587937393%2F%E6%AE%B5%E5%B4%87%E6%99%BA%E8%86%BA%E6%B3%B0%E6%99%A4%E5%A3%AB%E9%AB%98%E7%AD%89%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E7%89%A9-%E8%A9%95%E9%81%B8%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85-%E5%A0%85%E5%AE%9A%E7%82%BA%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E6%8C%BA%E8%BA%AB%E8%80%8C%E5%87%BA&h=303ff950\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191217/s00001/1576587937393/段崇智膺泰晤士高等教育風雲人物-評選記者-堅定為校園學生挺身而出</a><br />\n<br />\n《泰晤士高等教育》（Times Higher Education）今日（17日）公布2019年度全球高等教育風雲人物，香港中文大學校長段崇智榜上有名。評選的記者描述，香港所有大學領袖都被捲入示威風波，但沒太多像段崇智般堅定為他的校園及學生挺身而出。<br />\n《泰晤士高等教育》記者評選出11名對2019年高等教育界有影響力的學者或行政人員，其中關於段崇智的篇幅提到，新聞相片顯示段崇智11月中時，冒着危險到猶如戰場的中大校園，試圖使示威者與警方達成和平協議。衝突期間，警方透過大聲公呼籲「段校長及大學職員請立即離開，現在不是談判或者對話的時間」，之後就向段崇智的方向發射催淚彈。<br />\n《泰晤士高等教育》記者形容，未發生此事前，段崇智已經接觸不同學生，聆聽他們的不滿，同時呼籲停止暴力，即使被官方人士批評，仍然如一。該記者認為，中大是近日暴力事件中被破壞得最嚴重的兩間學校之一，段崇智來年主要的挑戰不是課室或實驗室，而是重建校園。<br />\n中大今日公布，校園和各項設施正逐漸修復，明年1月6日如期開學，同時繼續實施出入管制。<br />\n<br />\n講真 開頭佢真係有啲廢 問佢嘢又唔識答淨係遊花園 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係要知道 作為一個科學家 政治嘅嘢真係唔係佢嗰範<br />\n到最尾親自落場同班狗談判 仲要捱埋TG 入埋醫院<br />\n最後中大都無好似Poly咁俾狗圍足一個禮拜<br />\n佢真係應記一功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日睇番轉頭 我敢講佢係咁多間U最好嘅校長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前開口埋口都段狗段狗真係諗起都唔好意思<br />\n段爸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d155975082322b77a224934ffbf906b2d20a744","tid":1787092,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"段爸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5b8661f0255837336e996665e46be2a9ad2442f","tid":1787092,"uid":202612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:56:34.000Z","msg":"[行動置頂] 12.21 元朗x 多區商場和你shop 行動出爐啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1787075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1787075</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n勿忘721！"},{"pid":"8731558b45e358feae4148088567b184acabfea1","tid":1787092,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:57:08.000Z","msg":"KongU 共狗張翔正垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77c4b2aeb3f07db1775610d2a0a6a4594029a919","tid":1787092,"uid":325950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T15:57:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"251e6760a76c528b0ebe110087e8